flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: New invoice received and goods receipt recorded in SAP S/4HANA.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve purchase order details from SAP S/4HANA]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve goods receipt records from SAP S/4HANA]
  N2 --> N3[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve invoices from SAP S/4HANA]
  N3 --> N4[Stream: STREAMS - Perform three-way match using retrieved data]
  N4 --> N5{PB: Process Builder - Identify and resolve invoice discrepancies}
  N5 -->|Primary| N6[PB: Remote Functions - Correct goods receipt errors if any]
  N6 --> N7[PB: Remote Functions - Authorize supplier payments after successful verification]
  N7 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced working capital blocks, lower COGS leakage, and streamlined cash flow.]
  N5 -->|Invoice discrepancies detected| B1[Hold invoice and initiate discrepancy resolution process]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Invoice held for further review and resolution]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Goods receipt errors identified| B2[Initiate error correction workflow]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Errors corrected and records updated]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Successful three-way match| B3[Authorize payment to supplier]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Supplier payment authorized and processed]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]